    "guide": "<h3>🏖️ Best Beaches: At a Glance</h3><table class='beach-table'><thead><tr><th>Beach</th><th>Rating</th><th>Type</th><th>Facilities</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Skala Eressos</strong></td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</td><td>Grey Sand</td><td>Bohemian Hub</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Vatera</strong></td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</td><td>Long Sand</td><td>Infinite Space</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Agios Isidoros</strong></td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</td><td>Pebble</td><td>High-End</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Tarti</strong></td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐</td><td>Gold Sand</td><td>Fish Tavernas</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>📅 6-Day Odyssey Itinerary</h3><div class='itinerary-step'><strong>Day 1: Arrival (~10km).</strong> Collect car at the airport and head to Mytilene city.</div><div class='itinerary-step'><strong>Day 2: The North (~65km).</strong> Drive to the medieval village of Molyvos via the hot springs of Thermi.</div><div class='itinerary-step'><strong>Day 3: The West (~70km).</strong> Visit the Petrified Forest and stay in the bohemian Skala Eressos.</div><div class='itinerary-step'><strong>Day 4: Wetlands & Inland (~45km).</strong> Transition from West to South via Agiasos and Moni Limonos.</div><div class='itinerary-step'><strong>Day 5: Deep South (~80km).</strong> Raw hot springs at Polichnitos and the massive Vatera beach.</div><div class='itinerary-step'><strong>Day 6: The South & Departure (~120km).</strong> Visit Plomari ouzo distilleries, swim at Agios Isidoros, and head back to the airport.</div>"
